{"data": {"repository": {"pullRequest": {"id": "MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDg0ODAxNjE1", "number": 2538, "title": "Block Fields for Modding", "bodyText": "quickRotate: whether the block can be rotated with R(or Binding.rotateplaced) + Scroll Wheel.\nThis is because modded blocks are sometimes not meant to be rotated after placed, and a block cannot tell if it has been rotated unless it keeps track of its rotation, so in some cases it is better if the block is just not rotated at all after placed.\nrotateArrow: whether the block placement is guided by the arrow icon.\nThis is because some modded block are using the rotation of the block in an \"unintended\" way, such as making only whether it was vertically or horizontally placed count(a.k.a only rotation%2 matters), and in some cases it just makes sense to get rid of the arrow icon.", "createdAt": "2020-09-11T08:23:02Z", "url": "https://github.com/Anuken/Mindustry/pull/2538", "merged": true, "mergeCommit": {"oid": "b5b75656d11e3f73447d9b5961341152f0259d9f"}, "closed": true, "closedAt": "2020-09-12T14:11:10Z", "author": {"login": "sk7725"}, "timelineItems": {"totalCount": 10, "pageInfo": {"startCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdHwvA5AH2gAyNDg0ODAxNjE1OjI0MmJjYzA2Y2I1YzczYjBhYTY0MTBkMWVkODQ0MTE3MDNmYmNmZTg=", "endCursor": "Y3Vyc29yOnYyOpPPAAABdH2mcPAH2gAyNDg0ODAxNjE1OjE4MTNkNjg5NTU5MGNhNWQ5YTA0MGUyZmYyNTI4ZDY4ZjEyMTMzNjQ=", "hasNextPage": false, "hasPreviousPage": false}, "nodes": [{"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "242bcc06cb5c73b0aa6410d1ed84411703fbcfe8", "author": {"user": {"login": "sk7725", "name": "Sunny Kim"}}, "url": "https://github.com/Anuken/Mindustry/commit/242bcc06cb5c73b0aa6410d1ed84411703fbcfe8", "committedDate": "2020-09-11T08:01:30Z", "message": "quickRotate"}}, {"__typename": "PullRequestCommit", "commit": {"oid": "e93c5b42abcb2cb3148d76e5c231b1b6e53994d2", "author": {"user": {"login": "sk7725", "name": "Sunny Kim"}}, "url": "https://github.com/Anuken/Mindustry/commit/e93c5b42abcb2cb3148d7